            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新盤持續錄成交 黃金海灣．意嵐特色戶每呎1.3萬沽",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"新盤持續錄成交 黃金海灣．意嵐特色戶每呎1.3萬沽\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/25f7523efcc7c7d0484ac919d7e3a429/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050909410350356.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">新盤持續錄成交 黃金海灣．意嵐特色戶每呎1.3萬沽</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>新盤持續錄成交，旭日國際旗下位於屯門青山灣段的大型臨海項目黃金海灣．意嵐，昨日售出1伙連天台特色戶，為5B座26樓E室，開放式間隔，單位面積220方呎，天台面積179方呎，成交價290.2萬，呎價約13191元。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4238284/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃金海灣．意嵐連天台特色戶以290.2萬沽，每呎13191元。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fdcd9fea5efdf126dde435c0e47b4b53/2025-05/i_src_090252708.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃金海灣．意嵐連天台特色戶以290.2萬沽，每呎13191元。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>永泰旗下屯門現樓項目OMA by the Sea，昨日透過招標方式售出第2座17樓A9室，單位面積523方呎，連391方呎天台，2房間隔，成交價560萬，呎價約10707元。\n\n</p>\n<p>路勁旗下屯門現樓新盤凱和山，昨日錄得兩宗成交，最新售出單位包括第1座5樓H室，面積412方呎，成交價371.1萬，呎價約9007元，據悉買家為同區首置客。另售1座15樓D室，面積485方呎，成交價449.36萬，呎價約9265元，據悉買家為同區租客。\n\n</p><h2>啟德海灣呎價2.1萬</h2>\n<p>此外，由嘉華國際、會德豐地產及及中國海外合作發展的啟德海灣，昨日以招標方式售出第2A座29樓B單位，面積536方呎，2房連儲物室間隔，成交價1125.6萬，呎價約21000元。\n\n</p>\n<p>龍光及合景泰富合作發展的鴨脷洲豪宅凱玥，昨日亦錄招標成交，最新售出2座7樓B室，面積2604方呎，連車位以8100萬售出，呎價約31106元。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068017/即時-地產-新盤持續錄成交-黃金海灣-意嵐特色戶每呎1-3萬沽",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 09:56:42",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐協聯｜安東尼入世界波助貝迪斯躋身決賽 有機會歷史性1人奪2歐洲錦標",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"安東尼入世界波助貝迪斯躋身決賽，有機會歷史性1人奪2歐洲錦標。REUTERS/AP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3bbafd8090edb2f04501ca3aaa6cdb9e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050909344022321.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">安東尼入世界波助貝迪斯躋身決賽，有機會歷史性1人奪2歐洲錦標。REUTERS/AP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曼聯棄將安東尼馬菲奧斯持續有好表現，於周四的歐協聯4強次回合射入一個世界波，協助貝迪斯加時以4:3淘汰費倫天拿躋身決賽，將與車路士爭冠軍。由於安東尼上半季為曼聯在歐霸上陣，假若曼聯和貝迪斯都於歐霸和歐協聯決賽贏波，他便可歷史性一季同時奪得歐霸和歐協聯2個歐洲球會盃賽錦標。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(左)淘汰費倫天拿(右)入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3a9056686b8b0791dad7ca75e1392790/2025-05/2025-05-08T191601Z_821371152_UP1EL581HINRK_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-FIO-BET-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(左)淘汰費倫天拿(右)入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼為貝迪斯射入罰球。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/327ba8c8fb95ece6469d8aaf0b7b19e8/2025-05/2025-05-08T193559Z_1166522582_UP1EL581IFYSY_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-FIO-BET-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼為貝迪斯射入罰球。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼為貝迪斯射入罰球。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4d43e0af84179f0f20c872803aadd7bb/2025-05/Italy_Conference_League_Soccer_26319--eeb4a.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼為貝迪斯射入罰球。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"安東尼(右)為貝迪斯射入罰球。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6900e8d92565246577730744beb231b9/2025-05/2025-05-08T205026Z_174555076_UP1EL581LW1W3_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-FIO-BET-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        安東尼(右)為貝迪斯射入罰球。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(左)淘汰費倫天拿(右)入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8e88690581d20ab88a54972628d7a301/2025-05/2025-05-08T212330Z_624509494_UP1EL581NF5XW_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-FIO-BET-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(左)淘汰費倫天拿(右)入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"艾薩蘇利(左)為貝迪斯射入致勝球。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bec420aacadd279da2d2a07182b017b3/2025-05/2025-05-08T211932Z_22891115_UP1EL581N8IXT_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-FIO-BET-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        艾薩蘇利(左)為貝迪斯射入致勝球。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"艾薩蘇利為貝迪斯射入致勝球。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2e6c9508e319ed265e1c1a58a6c9a1a/2025-05/Italy_Conference_League_Soccer_56532--f3b1d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        艾薩蘇利為貝迪斯射入致勝球。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(圖)淘汰費倫天拿入歐協聯決賽。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c5c7562b3bef97972f059f373cfa9f9a/2025-05/Italy_Conference_League_Soccer_06802--09b89.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(圖)淘汰費倫天拿入歐協聯決賽。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝迪斯(圖)淘汰費倫天拿入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d8d1a11f3201d2927b619ad153af0bd/2025-05/2025-05-08T220843Z_1270397852_UP1EL581PC4YK_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-FIO-BET-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝迪斯(圖)淘汰費倫天拿入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>兩回合貢獻2球1助攻</h2>\n<p>歐協聯4強首回合貝迪斯主場對費倫天拿，安東尼為貝迪斯射入拉開至2:0的入球，最終贏2:1。今場次回合作客費倫天拿，安東尼又於30分鐘於禁區頂操刀罰球射入世界波，為貝迪斯先開紀錄；加時他又助攻予艾薩蘇利射入致勝球，全場交出1個入球、1次助攻以及3次關鍵傳送；兩回合共有2入球1助攻，成為球隊晉級決賽的重要功臣。\n\n</p><h2>安東尼兩邊叫胡</h2>\n<p>由於安東尼於上半季曾經為曼聯於歐霸上陣4場，若紅魔最終捧盃可以獲頒發冠軍獎牌。如今這名巴西翼鋒又領軍貝迪斯打入歐協聯決賽，假若貝迪斯又成功捧盃，他便可以成為歷史上首位於一季內奪得兩項歐洲球會盃賽錦標的球員。\n\n</p><h2>安東尼賽後激動落淚</h2>\n<p>安東尼於賽後激動落淚，他說：「比賽結束時我流了很多眼淚，我和我的媽媽、妻子、姊姊、弟弟，我們真的經歷了艱難時刻。完場時我十分激動，我的激動是因為喜悅，同時亦因為從困難中解脫，不單是球場上，還在我生活上經歷艱難的時刻。今場比賽十分困難，我們必須更加注意防守死球，不可以再犯同樣的錯誤。團隊的所有人，包括球員和工作人員今仗都很出色。」<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068016/即時-體育-歐協聯-安東尼入世界波助貝迪斯躋身決賽-有機會歷史性1人奪2歐洲錦標",
